<h3>Weddings</h3>
<p>Your wedding day is one of the most important and memorable days of your life. Start your life together celebrating in a venue that is elegant, romantic, vibrant and nothing short of magical. Our professional coordinators on hand will make sure your event is one of a kind and will be remembered forever. Leave all your worries with us and enjoy your day to the fullest.</p>
<span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-1 hover-type-none"><img width="800" image_height="600" image_id="1629" title="weddings" src="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/weddings.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-1629" srcset="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/weddings-200x150.jpg 200w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/weddings-400x300.jpg 400w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/weddings-600x450.jpg 600w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/weddings.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></span>
<h3>Engagement</h3>
<p>Aisshwarya Banquets is an elegant and royal venue to host engagement and reception ceremonies. The venue provides a host of options to our customers to choose between indoor banquet halls or outdoor lawn ceremonies. Be it your engagement with friends or family or a close knit affair for a small group of audience, we make it HAPPEN.</p>
<span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2 hover-type-none"><img width="800" image_height="600" image_id="1634" title="engement" src="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/engement.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-1634" srcset="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/engement-200x150.jpg 200w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/engement-400x300.jpg 400w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/engement-600x450.jpg 600w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/engement.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></span>
<h3>Reception</h3>
<p>When it comes to wedding receptions, we provide nothing but the very best decor, lip smacking food, groovy music and a wholesome ambience. While the bride and groom begin their journey of togetherness in presence of their friends and family, we leave no stone unturned to make this day memorable for you.</p>
<span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-3 hover-type-none"><img width="800" image_height="600" image_id="1635" title="reception" src="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/reception.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-1635" srcset="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/reception-200x150.jpg 200w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/reception-400x300.jpg 400w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/reception-600x450.jpg 600w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/reception.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></span>
</div><div class="nav fusion-mobile-tab-nav"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" id="mobile-fusion-tab-lifeevents" href="#tab-ba0c5c65070b295a434"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">Life Events</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-pane fade fusion-clearfix" id="tab-ba0c5c65070b295a434">
<p>Be it a baby shower or your kid&#8217;s first birthday party, elegant decor at Aisshwarya Banquets should be your first choice. Hold a grand wedding reception at one of the choicest banquet halls, we are the perfect destination to cater to every mood and every occasion close to your heart. We&#8217;ve got some of the best party packages you&#8217;ll ever find.</p>
<span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4 hover-type-none"><img width="800" image_height="600" image_id="1631" title="life-events" src="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/life-events.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-image-1631" srcset="../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/life-events-200x150.jpg 200w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/life-events-400x300.jpg 400w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/life-events-600x450.jpg 600w, ../wp-content/uploads/2020/08/life-events.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></span>
